          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679568182136-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry </strong>and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and cut into 1<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>rectangle per person</p><p>Score a 1cm border around the edge of the <strong>pastry rectangle[s] </strong>with a knife</p><p>Prick the inside of the border all over with a fork (this will stop you getting a soggy bottom!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1679568184841-x200.jpg",
