            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1679568187390-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>pastry rectangle[s]</strong> with the <strong>tomato base</strong>, spreading it out evenly, keeping it within the borders</p><p>Divide the <strong>softened aubergine </strong>equally between the pastry</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through and the edges have puffed up – this is your <strong>aubergine tart[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
